data.description: Beautiful home in the quiet and charming Hazelwood subdivision. Community streets are lined with mature trees and scenic walking paths that lead to 2 neighborhood parks, beckoning you to venture outdoors and appreciate the beauty of SW Boise's open skies. Main level features a lovely entry w/ wainscoting and hooks, large dining area, open kitchen-Family room w/ custom cabinets, slab granite, hardwood floors, SS appliances and fireplace. Upstairs features a large Master suite with dual vanities, and walk in closet, huge bonus room (or 4th bedroom) with closet and built in toy storage/bookcase, and 2 nicely-sized bedrooms. Backyard is huge and has two storage sheds and plenty of room to garden and romp. Landscape water is on  irrigation system which makes for very inexpensive summer watering bills. Beautiful 5 person cedar sauna is negotiable. HVAC is only a few years old and new carpet has just been installed throughout. Come see this welcoming home and see if it's meant to be yours!
